    "value": "Part-time community service work (average 20 hours per week) at non-profit/public facilities (e.g., schools, hospitals, day-care centers, senior centers); paid stipend at the highest of federal, state, or local minimum wage; job search assistance and guidance toward unsubsidized permanent employment.",
