  "application": {
    "methods": ["Phone: Operation ABLE (NH provider) - specific number not in results; national toll-free: 1-877-872-5627 (1-877-US2-JOBS)", "Online: CareerOneStop Older Worker Program Finder (national tool to locate NH providers)", "In-person: Contact local NH SCSEP provider such as Operation ABLE for offices"],
